OL,4,Cand won't 'speculate' on IRA details
OL,6,FGerry Adams has said an attempt is
OL,7,Fbeing made to "smother" the jury in
OL,8,Fhistory as he was questioned over his
OL,9,Fpast statements and events during the
OL,10,FTroubles.
OL,12,FThe former Sinn Fein leader faced
OL,13,Fcross-examination over his knowledge
OL,14,Fof who was in the IRA and the
OL,15,Forganisation's rules, on which he
OL,16,Frepeatedly said he would not
OL,17,F"speculate" in court.
