OL,3,CAdams says informer comment 'harsh'
OL,4,Cand won't 'speculate' on IRA details
OL,6,FMr Adams is continuing to give
OL,7,Fevidence in his defamation case
OL,8,Fagainst the BBC at the High Court in
OL,9,FDublin.
OL,11,FHe claims a BBC Spotlight programme,
OL,12,Fand an accompanying online story,
OL,13,Fdefamed him by alleging he sanctioned
OL,14,Fthe killing of the former Sinn Fein
OL,15,Fofficial Denis Donaldson.
OL,17,FMr Donaldson, who had worked for Sinn
OL,18,FFein, was shot dead in Donegal in
OL,19,F2006, months after admitting his role
OL,20,Fas a police and MI5 agent for 20 years.
