OL,6,FMr Adams denies any involvement.
OL,8,FIn 2009, the Real IRA admitted killing
OL,9,FMr Donaldson.
OL,11,FThe Spotlight programme was broadcast
OL,12,Fin September 2016.
OL,14,FThe trial opened last week with
OL,15,Fbarrister for Mr Adams, Tom Hogan SC,
OL,16,Fsaying the former Sinn Fein
OL,17,Fpresident's reputation as a
OL,18,F"peacemaker" had suffered an
OL,19,F"unjustified" attack because of the
OL,20,Fbroadcast of the BBC programme.
