OL,3,CAdams says informer comment 'harsh'
OL,4,Cand won't 'speculate' on IRA details
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, Mr Adams entered the
OL,7,Fwitness box for a fifth day.
OL,9,FThe jury was shown a montage of
OL,10,Fvarious broadcast footage of
OL,11,Finterviews with figures such as Peter
OL,12,FMcMullan, who said he was a former IRA
OL,13,Fmember who worked with Mr Adams in the
OL,14,FBelfast brigade.
OL,16,FThe jury were also shown a video clip
OL,17,Fof Mr Adams from 1987 where he was
OL,18,Fasked about the death of Charles
OL,19,FMcIlmurray.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
