OL,3,CAdams says informer comment 'harsh'
OL,4,Cand won't 'speculate' on IRA details
OL,6,F"Mr McIlmurray, like anyone living in
OL,7,FWest Belfast knows, that the
OL,8,Fconsequence of informing is death," he
OL,9,Fsaid in the clip.
OL,11,FUnder cross-examination from Mr
OL,12,FGallagher, Mr Adams said his remark
OL,13,Fwas "very harsh" but was made along
OL,14,Fwith other comments at a press
OL,15,Fconference including expressing his
OL,16,Fcommiserations with the family of Mr
OL,17,FMcIlmurray.
OL,19,FHe denied that the statement was made
OL,20,Fas a warning or a threat, or that he
OL,21,Fwas attributing blame to Mr McIlmurray.
