OL,3,CAdams says informer comment 'harsh'
OL,4,Cand won't 'speculate' on IRA details
OL,6,FMr Gallagher asked him several times
OL,7,Fif he was aware of the structures and
OL,8,Frules of the IRA, to which Mr Adams
OL,9,Fsaid several times he would not
OL,10,F"speculate" in court and had already
OL,11,Fanswered the question.
OL,13,F"I don't intend to speculate on any of
OL,14,Fthose issues in relation to the IRA,"
OL,15,FMr Adams said.
OL,17,FWhen pressed on whether he was not
OL,18,Fgoing to answer any questions in
OL,19,Frelation to the IRA, Mr Adams said an
OL,20,Fattempt was made to "smother them (the
OL,21,Fjury) in an awful history".
