OL,3,CAdams says informer comment 'harsh'
OL,4,Cand won't 'speculate' on IRA details
OL,6,F"What on earth has this got to do with
OL,7,FDenis Donaldson," Mr Adams said.
OL,9,FMr Adams said he could not comment on
OL,10,Fwhy people including informers were
OL,11,F'disappeared' during the Troubles, but
OL,12,Fcalled it "horrific".
OL,14,F"It was wrong, bad enough that
OL,15,Finformers were being killed, but to
OL,16,Fdisappear their bodies was totally and
OL,17,Fabsolutely wrong."
OL,19,FHe told the court he believes he had
OL,20,Fmet all the families of those who were
OL,21,Fshot and secretly buried by the IRA.
