OL,3,CAdams says informer comment 'harsh'
OL,4,Cand won't 'speculate' on IRA details
OL,6,FMr Adams, 76, stepped down as Sinn
OL,7,FFein president in 2018 after 34 years
OL,8,Fat the helm.
OL,10,FHe served as an MP for West Belfast
OL,11,Fand represented the Louth constituency
OL,12,Fin the Dail parliament until the 2020
OL,13,Fgeneral election, when he retired from
OL,14,Fpolitics.
OL,16,FThe trial, which is expected to last
OL,17,Ffour weeks, continues.
